    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192110/extras/1726d27d8f583f4e1c029b5b703af36a.avif?t=1769122958\" width=780 height=439 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend the Tower Against Enemy Invasions!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Your mission:</strong></i> protect the tower and its battle flag from relentless enemies. If the enemy reaches the top of the tower where the flag is located, the tower is considered captured.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your heavenly magic sword to eliminate groups of enemies of the same color with precise strikes. Take advantage of powerful bonuses to enhance your combat efficiency, but beware of negative effects that can hinder your progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your resources wisely, as they might be limited, and ensure every shot counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes three difficulty modes: easy, medium, hard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game features an action-packed journey with <strong>60 challenging levels</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completing levels doesn't always depend on your skills, you also need luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to defend your tower and claim victory? The battle awaits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192110/extras/56c7f30f2e03fb2e1b2bfd22c93d5531.avif?t=1769122958\" width=780 height=485 /></span></p>",
